		</a>
		<h1 class="title">一个演了 2000 多场《剧院魅影》的音乐剧演员，和我们聊了聊他的百老汇人生</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/73/small/73.jpg?1415670876" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">俞斯译 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-05-15 15:40:01 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
		<img src="/system/articles/longshows/9635/medium/9635.jpeg?1431672893" alt="" />
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="9635" data-title="《一个演了 2000 多场《剧院魅影》的音乐剧演员，和我们聊了聊他的百老汇人生》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9635/medium/9635.jpg?1436675261" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9635.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
